steps.instruction:
Made by Andy Baraghani and can be found [here](https://www.bonappetit.com/recipe/cashew-yogurt)

### Prep
- Soak the cashews overnight, then drain them

### Steps
1. Purée cashews, lemon juice, salt, and 2 tsp. honey in a blender. With the motor running, stream in ½–⅔ cup water until smooth and the cashews are a similar texture to yogurt.
2. Transfer to a medium bowl. Top with fruit and/or nuts, then drizzle with honey.

ingredients.note: Or agave nectar, plus more for serving
